 "html": "<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-5355\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"hot cross bun poeding\" width=\"530\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-600x450.jpeg 600w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-300x225.jpeg 300w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-768x576.jpeg 768w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-750x563.jpeg 750w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-500x375.jpeg 500w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-380x285.jpeg 380w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-760x570.jpeg 760w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00-800x600.jpeg 800w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.50.00.jpeg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"></p>\n<p>Met Paasfees om die draai is dit tyd om iets met die hot cross buns te maak.</p>\n<h3>Bestanddele</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>6 hot cross buns</li>\n<li>Appelkooskonfyt</li>\n<li>Botter</li>\n<li>500 ml room</li>\n<li>1 blikkie Idealmelk</li>\n<li>250 ml melk</li>\n<li>125 ml strooisuiker</li>\n<li>5 eiers</li>\n<li>5 ml karamelgeursel (vanilla essence)</li>\n<li>Flake sjokolades</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-5357\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53-768x1024.jpeg\" alt=\"hot cross buns\" width=\"530\" height=\"707\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53-768x1024.jpeg 768w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53-600x800.jpeg 600w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53-225x300.jpeg 225w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53-750x1000.jpeg 750w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53-380x507.jpeg 380w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53-760x1013.jpeg 760w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53-800x1067.jpeg 800w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.53.jpeg 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"></h3>\n<h3>Metode</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Sny die hot cross buns deur en smeer ruim met botter en appelkooskonfyt.</li>\n<li>Pak dit soos dakteels oormekaar in n gesmeerde oondbak.</li>\n<li>Klits die res van die bestandele (behalwe die flakes) saam en giet oor die hot cross buns.</li>\n<li>Laat dit n halfuur staan om in te trek.</li>\n<li>Bak oop vir 40 min by 180 grade celsius.</li>\n<li>Strooi flakes oor en eet met roomys of vla.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-5356\" src=\"/media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-1024x768.jpeg\" alt=\"hot cross bun poeding\" width=\"530\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-1024x768.jpeg 1024w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-600x450.jpeg 600w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-300x225.jpeg 300w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-768x576.jpeg 768w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-750x563.jpeg 750w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-500x375.jpeg 500w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-380x285.jpeg 380w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-760x570.jpeg 760w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58-800x600.jpeg 800w, /media/uploads/2019/03/WhatsApp-Image-2019-03-25-at-21.49.58.jpeg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"></p>",
